def remove_duplicates(nums):
    nums.sort()
    current = 1
    next_unique = 1
    while next_unique < len(nums):
        if nums[current] != nums[next_unique]:
            current += 1
            nums[current] = nums[next_unique]
        next_unique += 1
    del nums[current + 1:]
    return nums
